    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8, delivering 414 hp with a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS step-less camshaft timing. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the weight-saving factory carbon fiber roof. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator preventative services already performed. Zero cosmetic imperfections, original factory finish, and an interior with no discernible bolster wear or trim degradation. A true collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
