      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, preserved in pristine showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips, highlighting the meticulous care it has received. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather remains supple and retains that distinct new-car scent, with every electronic component and switch functioning exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive logbook to document its pampered history. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled environment, this car represents a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
